Bugfixes:
 - Create runtime directories if they do not exist (Richard Hughes)
 - Do not crash when there are no devices to return (Richard Hughes)

Version 0.1.0
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Released: 2015-03-16

Notes:
 - fwupd is a simple daemon to allow session software to update firmware.
